 1- yạ ạ̹lhy yạ ạ̹lhy .. lạ rjạʾ ly swạk
 tạq qlby tạq lby .. ạ̉n ạ̉fwz brḍạk
 ạlqrạr- mlʾ rwḥk ạ̹sẖtyạqy .. hbh ly wạ̉str kẖṭạy
 yrtwy̱ mnh gẖlyly .. fyk lạ gẖyr rjạy
 2- ạ̉nt rby nwr qlby .. ạ̉nt ḥṣn ạ̉tqyạk
 fạ̉mlạn yạ rb qlby .. rwḥ qdsiⁿ mn ʿlạk
 3- qlby ạ̉mlạ rwḥ ḥbiⁿ .. rwḥ briⁿ wslạm
 rwḥ ạ̹ymạniⁿ wṣbriⁿ .. rwḥ lṭfiⁿ wwỷạm
 4- mlʾ rwḥk ḥyạty .. mlʾ rwḥk ạlwdyʿ
 mlʾ rwḥk ạmnḥny .. yạ yswʿ yạ smyʿ</lyrics>
